.TH "libnvme_mi_open_mctp" 9 "libnvme_mi_open_mctp" "April 2026" "libnvme API manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
libnvme_mi_open_mctp \- Create an endpoint using a MCTP connection.
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "libnvme_mi_ep_t" libnvme_mi_open_mctp
.BI "(struct libnvme_global_ctx *ctx "  ","
.BI "unsigned int netid "  ","
.BI "uint8_t eid "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "ctx" 12
\fIstruct libnvme_global_ctx\fP object
.IP "netid" 12
MCTP network ID on this system
.IP "eid" 12
MCTP endpoint ID
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Transport-specific endpoint initialization for MI-connected endpoints. Once
an endpoint is created, the rest of the API is transport-independent.

See \fIlibnvme_mi_close\fP
.SH "RETURN"
New endpoint object for \fInetid\fP & \fIeid\fP, or NULL on failure.
